A3. Discover security concepts used in your house.
The security concept that is used in my house is the Wifi password. To access the wifi i have to know 
the secret password that i've created to log into into my network and connect devices that I want. 
This security system prevents anybody from outside 
(neighbour or wifi thief) to access my network where they can use my exposed IPs of devices connected to perform certain type of attacks.